  "text": "Larger rooms with more empty space are inclined to have more particles in resuspension resultant from simple physical activities, such as walking [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ). This has been supported by the current study since the classrooms with higher squared meters per child showed higher concentrations of UFPs in a significant correlated proportion.",
